spec_data.Name: perl-interpreter
spec_data.Description:
This is a Perl interpreter as a standalone executable /usr/bin/perl
required for handling Perl scripts. It does not provide all the other Perl
modules or tools.

This is a dummy package for compatibility with Fedora source packages. The
Perl interpreter is provided by perl package. See
<https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Changes/perl_Package_to_Install_Core_Modules>
and <https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1410347>.
